{"tid":862121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁正常，真係好唔正常","createTime":"2018-10-14T15:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:24:45.000Z","uid":179824,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"884eab9471caf77d9d62c126679b905b4ac061d3","tid":862121,"uid":179824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"我認我衰女，父母死攔住我唔畀我出去我冇去<br />\n但係起碼我有做鍵盤戰士有去留cm，就算出唔到去都希望出一份力 ，keep住留意前線巴絲的動向<br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇成個ig story都係飲飲食食，去OP玩哈囉喂，周日旅行，碌咗差唔多幾十個人嘅story先見到一個有談論到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常到好似根本冇事發生咁<br />\n談論到遊行甚至有friend問我有咩遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雨革嘅時候唔係咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解？<br />\n你哋見到香港依家禮崩樂壞良心唔會不安㗎咩？唔會心痛？唔會想守護？<br />\n<br />\n依家輾轉反側，良心受到極大譴責，我仲有咩可以做到可以幫到你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0050996d8fea7adff139d4f2c8f4df4e0e3b1081","tid":862121,"uid":16584,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"啱呀屌那星 成個ig都係全民造星<br />\n香港人唔配有民主"},{"pid":"377127bc6b51c5d9c4cba9937e2a5286708bd3ba","tid":862121,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲 唔理你依加喺屋企又好 定喺美國領事館 一齊去美國領事嘅Facebook 同 Twitter 留言洗版！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/317451486051/posts/10156920430356052/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F317451486051%2Fposts%2F10156920430356052%2F&d=PQpYiLKs5yqNXY%2FlP%2FnCgcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=91350181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/317451486051/posts/10156920430356052/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/usainhkmacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fusainhkmacau&d=PQpYiLKs5yqNXY%2FlP%2FnCgcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3add7416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.co